      <title>特朗普政府驳回了两名民主党FTC专员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/trump-administration-dismisses-two-democratic-ftc-commissioners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府周二在美国联邦贸易委员会上驳回了两名民主党人，这是关于对美国机构进行控制的最新例子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/trump-administration-dismisses-two-democratic-ftc-commissioners</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 21:15:28 GMT</pubDate>
